<div class="mainContainer">
  <div class="textDiv">
    <h2>CRTV JAM — Your Weekly Creative Escape</h2>
    <p class="sectionText">
      CRTV Jam is our ongoing creative escape. Every week we touch down in a new
      city — this week: Berlin. The walls, the streets, the hidden corners and
      loud voices become our inspiration, transformed into prompts that spark
      new ideas.
    </p>
    <p class="sectionText">
      Three times a week — Monday, Wednesday, Friday — we drop a fresh prompt
      connected to the place we're in. That word or phrase is your invitation to
      create. What you make is entirely up to you: a quick sketch, a photo roll,
      a stitched pattern, a home-cooked dish, a digital remix, a mural, a
      melody. There are no limits, only openings.
    </p>
    <p class="sectionText">
      When you're ready, share it with us. If you want the spotlight, we'll tag
      you and put your name out there. If you'd rather stay behind the curtain,
      we'll post it anonymously. This way you can explore freely, whether you're
      an upcoming artist searching for exposure or someone testing the waters of
      your own creativity.
    </p>
    <p class="sectionText">
      Every Sunday we gather the week's creations and showcase them side by
      side. The result is a collective canvas: a snapshot of how one city can be
      reimagined in a hundred different ways. CRTV Jam isn't about perfection.
      It's about process, play, and finding new ways to escape through making.
      Join us, and turn the next prompt into your own creative jam.
    </p>
    <p class="sectionText"></p>
  </div>
